				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=27600&amp;sid=60d53ff64cfa5af9da1d766833156c56#27600"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Sun Jun 15, 2003 3:09 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: What do you think of this idea to improve survival?</span></td>
				<td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=27600&amp;sid=60d53ff64cfa5af9da1d766833156c56"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a> <a href="posting.php?mode=editpost&amp;p=27600&amp;sid=60d53ff64cfa5af9da1d766833156c56"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_edit.gif" alt="Edit/Delete this post" title="Edit/Delete this post" border="0" /></a>  </td>
