				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It is not that sorcerers are too weak. Infact they are the most powerfull casterclass in the game. I don't want to play any other class, because none combines the ability to nuke, root, mezz, debuff with speed and a level 50 pet. Each ability for one might be laughable nowadays but the combination is unique. And therefore the guy with  the discostar is the primary target.
<br />
Our  problem is, that tanks are too strong. A RR8+ Tank is almost invulnerable. Take Det, Purge, 2 full healthbars, 2 full endubars,  AoM ........ and to make it even worth, they even have CCs like stun and prevent flight.  
<br />
That's ridiculous.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
