				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">An easy thing to do for Mythic would be to add more pets in heavy populated rvr areas that cast spells.
<br />

<br />
Forest Sauvage could have some high level pets
<br />

<br />
Emain Macha could have more to choose from than Grogans, Granny's, goberchands
<br />

<br />
Odins Gate actually has a few good pets
<br />

<br />
Isalf's, Bright Aurora, cats, lots of weird undead things (names escape me atm).
<br />

<br />
Another huge issue is the amount of (Under) level 20 area's there are in the game.
<br />

<br />
Half of all three realms are newbie zones.
<br />

<br />
Take Albion (Ther are a lot of under level 20 zones)
<br />
Excluding dungeons
<br />
10 under 20
<br />
10 over 20
<br />

<br />
Zones under 20
<br />
Camelot Hills
<br />
South Black Mountains
<br />
North Black Mountains
<br />
Salisbury Plains
<br />
