<br />
Cornwall
<br />
Forest Sauvage
<br />
Gothwaite Harbor
<br />
Isle of Glass
<br />
Lynn Barfog (for the majority of the area)
<br />
Dales of Devwy
<br />

<br />
Zones over level 20
<br />
Lyonesse
<br />
Dartmoor
<br />
Pennine Mountains
<br />
Hadrians Wall
<br />
Lynn Barfog (Only high level epic mobs and some others)
<br />
Snowdonia
<br />
Avalon Isle
<br />
Dales of Devwy
<br />
Gwyddneau
<br />
Caldey
<br />
Aldland
<br />

<br />
IMO, some of the under 20 zones desperately need to be increased.  With the vast majority of people creating characters at level 20 or 30...who needs these zones now ?!?</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
